       <div class="content"> 
        <p>I really appreciate this post- as someone who is 100% on board with the project, I still did not fully understand the gravity of the situation and how contaminated the water was and its overall affects. As a non-engineer and non-scientist, I appreciate the easy to understand explanation of the project and the outcomes. The work of the group and how much you accomplished in such a short amount of time is both impressive and inspiring. I am so excited- great strides in research and hands-on work at VMI, an illustration of what being a citizen-soldier is all about, and providing much needed and deserved clean natural resources to Pampoyo. I love this. You have my support VMI EWB!</p> 
